questions.quote: Yeah, what're you saying, you just sort of put away feelings or whatever the hell it was you felt for me?
You guys do that? Chandler won't even have sex in our bathroom!
Yeah, I read some great applications, but then I thought "who better then a minister to raise a child!"
Really? So, you're gonna stick with this 'it's all for her' thing?
Y'know, you-you also could've used uh, lamps and then followed the light.
You don't know how long we're gonna be in here! We may have to repopulate the Earth.
Oh, you uh, you wanna hear a freaky coincidence? Guess who's doing laundry there too?
Yeah, y'know what? I'm-I'm gonna meet you upstairs in a minute.
Woha! Wait... What are we doing? What we have is too important to mess it up over some girl. I mean, we can get laid anytime we want.
